    <h3 class="contentListingItemTitle"><a href="https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article/522/4/6236/7159739">JWST NIRCam + NIRSpec: interstellar medium and stellar populations of young galaxies with rising star formation and evolving gas reservoirs</a></h3>
       <div class="contributors">Sandro Tacchella, Benjamin D Johnson, Brant E Robertson and others</div>
        
       
       <div class="location">
          
          <div class="citation"><em>Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society</em>, Volume 522, Issue 4, July 2023, Pages 6236–6249, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stad1408">https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stad1408</a></div>
