       <div class="contributors">Sharon Lapiner, Avishai Dekel, Jonathan Freundlich, Omri Ginzburg, Fangzhou Jiang, Michael Kretschmer, Sandro Tacchella, Daniel Ceverino, Joel Primack</div>
        
       
       <div class="location">
          
          <div class="citation"><em>Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society</em>, Volume 522, Issue 3, July 2023, Pages 4515–4547, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stad1263">https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stad1263</a></div>
