       <div class="contributors">Minjung Park, Sandro Tacchella, Erica J Nelson, Lars Hernquist, Rainer Weinberger, Benedikt Diemer, Dylan Nelson, Annalisa Pillepich, Federico Marinacci, Mark Vogelsberger</div>
        
       
       <div class="location">
          
          <div class="citation"><em>Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society</em>, Volume 515, Issue 1, September 2022, Pages 213–228, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stac1773">https://doi.org/10.1093/mnras/stac1773</a></div>
       </div>
       
       

        

       
